        "TileImage": "$($repository bd0689d6-07b4-4757-b8ee-cac19f1c9e16).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to Las Vegas, 47. There&apos;s a white supremacist from Africa, his name is Zana Kazem, who is trying to sell some DNA material and lab reports to the wealthy Omar Al-Ghazali. The sheikh is working for someone else, but we&apos;re not sure who. Our client wants to force them into the open by disrupting the deal. You&apos;ve got three targets:the Vulture, the Sheikh, and the Scientist, who&apos;ll be there to verify the material. We&apos;ve been losing a lot of agents lately, 47. Be careful and  good luck.",
